<paragraph id="099BB766A6F8C570E336BF1A2EB827A9" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
<taxonomicName id="FE4554A9D3880BB9BE478936B0BC1896" authorityName="C. Cusset, Fl. Cameroun 30: 94" authorityYear="1987" baseAuthorityName="Engl." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Podostemaceae" genus="Saxicolella" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Saxicolella laciniata" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="laciniata">
<emphasis id="5655FE713738930509C7D7F1FE463836" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Saxicolella laciniata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is listed on http://www.iucnredlist.org as Vulnerable (
<bibRefCitation id="EECA92E47E7E53769C4BCF07AC6B29BE" DOI="https://doi.org/10.2305/IUCN.UK.2010-3.RLTS.T185310A8386482.en" author="Ghogue, J-P" journalOrPublisher="Botanical Journal of the Linnean Society" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" refId="B44" refString="Ghogue, J-P, 2010p. Saxicolellalaciniata. The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species 2010: e.T185310A8386482. https://doi.org/10.2305/IUCN.UK.2010-3.RLTS.T185310A8386482.en" title="Saxicolellalaciniata. The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species 2010: e. T 185310 A 8386482." url="https://doi.org/10.2305/IUCN.UK.2010-3.RLTS.T185310A8386482.en" year="2010 p">Ghogue 2010p</bibRefCitation>
). It was assessed in 
<bibRefCitation id="C343D7027096F1D8826E7B7C8FEC4526" author="Onana, JM" journalOrPublisher="Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" refId="B66" refString="Onana, JM, Cheek, M, 2011. Red data list of the flowering plants of Cameroon: IUCN Global Assessments. Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew" title="Red data list of the flowering plants of Cameroon: IUCN Global Assessments." year="2011">Onana and Cheek (2011)</bibRefCitation>
as Endangered. The taxon is known from two localities. The extent of occurrence is estimated at 2 km2 and the area of occupancy is 8 km2. The main threats at the localities are forest exploitation for agriculture purposes. The species is here reassessed and the Endangered status maintained. IUCN Red List Category: 
<emphasis id="7CB83C6EA10395A22FAC839A254906B0" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Endangered ENB2ab (iii).</emphasis>
</paragraph>
